  <p>
    The <tt>laurel</tt> application attempts to provide tools to assist with
    <tt>image captioning</tt>
    within the context of
    <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Machine_learning">machine learning</a>.
  </p>
  <p>
    In particular, the application is geared towards the management of smaller datasets (in the range of thousands of
    images) for use in techniques such as
    <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fine-tuning_(deep_learning)#Low-rank_adaptation">LORA</a>
    training.
